(22, 22, '重庆装修_装修流程_装修步骤-【模范家】', '重庆装修,装修一般流程,装修步骤', '重庆模范家为您详细的讲解装修的一般流程，让您能够了解装修的每一个步骤，以及装修每一步要做好如何的验收。', '<p>\r\n	确定装修公司后，具体的装修施工流程是：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<table style="width:522.55pt;border-collapse:collapse;" class="MsoNormalTable" align="center">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">去物业申请装修许可证</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">带现金交装修押金</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">向物业申请墙体改动点</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">动工遵守相关规定</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">一般还要准备临时灭火筒</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="696" colspan="3">\r\n					<p style="text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;" class="p" align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">水电现场定位交底</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">插座尽量多预留</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">理论结合设计现场粉笔定位</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">电视背后插座可考虑藏在柜内</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">客厅、房间、走道尽量留双控</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">根据厨卫布局安排给水排水位置</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">马桶、水槽下、鞋柜内、弱电箱</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">等地方尽量预留插座备用</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">问清楚是否包括后期插座面板安装</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">如开发商已经做好，根据实际适当增加修改即可无需全改</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">有较多的电工专题建议</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">瓷砖商工地量尺、订货、确定铺贴方案、出图。</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">波导线、地脚线</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">墙砖地砖、窗台石</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">门槛石、背景墙</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">砖砌橱柜洗手台</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">都可能用到瓷砖</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">在一家店订购砍价更实惠</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">主体拆改</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">与物业充分沟通</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">不动主力墙</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">避免长距离横向开槽</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">凿地脚线槽、开线槽</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">部分电工泥工都不包开槽的了</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">新建墙体</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">（挂网）</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">完全没必要全屋挂网</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">局部新旧墙体之间挂网即可</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">房屋沉降导致的墙体开裂挂网也没用</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">水电材料进场</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">核实数量尤其是电线</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">提醒师傅减少浪费</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">未用材料一般可退</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">留个心眼小心被掉包</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">订购木地板、壁纸、吊顶、</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">木工板材</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">选款式对比价格留电话写备注</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">所有的“限期活动”都是障眼法</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">不急不燥不贪便宜不交钱</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">封闭阳台</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">咨询物业有无要求</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">先装好窗体框架</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">等贴完砖之后搞好卫生再装玻璃。</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">更换</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">入户门</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">根据水电管道高度找出地面水平</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">入户门高度比客厅地面高<span>15mm</span><span>为宜</span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">先装好入户门泥水工容易瓷砖收边</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">不用再回头返工</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">水电完工验收</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:baseline;" class="p" align="justify">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">PPR<span>管打压实验</span><span>0.8~1M/Pa</span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:baseline;" class="p" align="justify">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">半小时压降<span>0.05</span><span>内为合格</span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:baseline;" class="p" align="justify">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">插座开关底盒无明显变形错位</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:baseline;" class="p" align="justify">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">管道无错乱交叠，地面尽量活线</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:justify;vertical-align:baseline;" class="p" align="justify">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">有问题不要犹豫不怕麻烦要求返工</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="696" colspan="3">\r\n					<p style="text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal" align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;background:#548dd4;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">联系泥水工看场地、议价</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;background:#548dd4;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">、进场</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">最好看过师傅手艺才联系</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">要做好细节的沟通避免加价</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">按天算<span>/</span><span>按项目算</span><span>/</span><span>整套承包</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">比价最好参考当地一天工价结合工期评估</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">菜单栏也有泥水工钱调研结果供大家参考</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">木工进场(吊顶、柜等等）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">理论上木工和泥水工可以同时进场</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">但是堆太多材料非常影响双方的施工质量</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">建议泥水师傅先完工再进木工</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">木工材料跟师傅沟通即可</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">注意问清楚各种柜的计价方式再动工</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">瓷砖到货验收、铺贴交底</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">当场检查全部瓷砖不现实</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">跟师傅强调：存在色差、破损、明显不平整、不方正等问题</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">要把瓷砖单独空出来进行退换</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">贴砖到边角难免出现难看的小砖</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">叮嘱师傅把边角留在隐蔽的地方</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">先从显眼处开始贴<span>,</span><span>把收尾的砖放在隐蔽处更美观</span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">厨卫</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">阳台</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">门</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">安装</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">、门槛石、</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">淋浴</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">挡水石、窗台石量尺</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">先装好厨卫阳台门才贴地砖</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">门槛石、淋浴房挡水石</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">窗台石可以安排量尺定制</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">一般<span>4~7</span><span>天可以到货</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">铝合金窗</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">到货安装</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">如果要更换铝合金窗</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">泥工退场前完成最佳</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">边框内外都要打好结构胶</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;background:#548dd4;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">厨卫门槛石安装</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">如果是木地板的房间</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">最好先装门槛石再做防水</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">防水施工验收（闭水试验）</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">搞好地面卫生很重要</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">做二次排水坡向排水管</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">涂料防水要等干透才可以刷第二遍</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">蓄水闭水实验一般要<span>72</span><span>小时</span></span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">本人、物业、楼下业主共同验收</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">订购油烟机、消毒柜、燃气灶、水槽。</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">不同品牌的电器尺寸一般不同</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">确定了后很难修改，所以确定后一般不改</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">消毒柜、燃气灶开孔、预留尺寸提前告诉商家</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">水槽最好提前买回来，推荐<span>304</span><span>不锈钢材质</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">交给橱柜商家定制橱柜台面</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">建议做台中盆或者台下盆</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="696" colspan="3">\r\n					<p style="text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal" align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">墙砖铺贴完毕验收</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">阳角处理可以选：阳角条、<span>45</span><span>度碰角、抛光砖单边磨圆</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">最好每天都到工地检查问题</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">发现问题马上返工成本最低</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">重点检查空鼓问题（敲听声音）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">有掉落伤人风险处墙砖空鼓一定返工</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">常走的过道地砖空鼓一定返工</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">要留<span>1mm</span><span>以上砖缝避免冷缩热涨挤压</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">瓷砖返工比较麻烦但一定要坚持</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">门槛石窗台大理石到货安装</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">到货仔细检查有无破损裂痕</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">石纹纹路对口无明显色差</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">接缝及边缘处仔细检查</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">要及时清理表面卫生</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">不做窗线要注意预留刮腻子和乳胶漆的厚度</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">避免由于水泥凸起无法做收口</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">厨柜复尺，及签订加工合同</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">厨房墙地砖完工后进行</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">提供水槽实物</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">提供炉灶、拉篮等电器五金尺寸</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">最好根据业主身高定台面高度</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">按照洗、切、炒进行规划</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">问清楚总价、各项收费标准</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">泥水活基本完成，安排补砖</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">、</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">地砖填缝</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">。</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">补砖之前一定仔细搜刮现场</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">经常出现有剩砖时盲目补砖的问题</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">补砖要注意色差问题</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">如果准备美缝，注意填缝留<span>2mm</span><span>以上的深度</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">趁未干用布擦去多余的填缝剂（擦深一点）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="696" colspan="3">\r\n					<p style="text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal" align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">木工进行时</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">吊顶、房门、门窗套、背景墙造型</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">各种柜子、卡座、床、楼梯</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">提前跟师傅沟通有割坏的板材</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">根据家庭实际需要设计衣柜柜内分隔</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">固定在墙上的家具要考虑<span>5</span><span>年之内是否有改动才做</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">现在渐渐是生态板<span>+</span><span>钉子</span><span>+</span><span>收边条为主流</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">板材表面<span>+</span><span>实木贴皮</span><span>+</span><span>油漆效果更好，更复杂更贵</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">木工现场甲醛、<span>VOCs</span><span>浓度高，务必注意防护</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">孕妇小孩不建议到现场参观</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">建议减少木工定制多买实木成品家具</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">板材都会有甲醛释放、油漆都会有<span>VOCs</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">只有实木<span>+</span><span>清漆的有害物质挥发周期较短</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">提醒师傅注意作业现场通风（刷漆时要避免扬尘除外）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">木工完工验收</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">木工验收基本都是眼见功夫</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">破损、污渍、缺角、缝隙</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">检查各种五金（合页轨道）等是否顺利开关</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">留一定的余量保证板材冷缩热涨的影响</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">衣柜如果是另外定制的双柜门（未安装）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">柜内抽屉避开中线<span>5cm</span><span>以上才不会被柜门挡住</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">瑕疵可以用钉眼灰或家具修复蜡笔处理</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">结算工资前一定要确保所有问题解决</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">石膏线进场</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">可做吊顶、背景墙、垭口</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">检查花纹精细度、气孔多的为次品</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">性价比较高的材料、施工周期短</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">完工后表面需刷乳胶漆</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">厨卫吊顶</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">上门量尺，定方案</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">PVC<span>扣板、铝合金扣板、防潮石膏板</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">推荐用铝扣板（耐用、施工难度较低）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">厚度选择<span>0.6~0.8mm</span><span>即可</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">重点确认其他辅料的价格（让其报总价）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">边线、铝梁、灯、浴霸、是否包安装费</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">确认配套电器价格、尺寸（有些是特殊尺寸买不到）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">设计考虑好烟机位置（遮挡部分效果）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">干湿分离等空间细节（空间分割）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">定制类家具上门测量</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">各种柜、地台、吧台、卡座</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">注意报价的项目是否完整</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">应包含柜门、镜子、五金类、相关配套</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">位置注意避开开关插座面板</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">定制到顶衣柜需要注意顶部缝隙</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">先做好衣柜再做吊顶，否则容易有收边难看问题</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="696" colspan="3">\r\n					<p style="text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal" align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">购买开关插座面板、灯具、花洒、水龙头、角阀、下水管。</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">网上京东天猫旗舰店是正品（收货若有瑕疵品可以退）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">实体店买面板拿上手对比重量是个直观有用的对比方法</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">中高端：<span>ABB</span><span>、西蒙、西门子、施耐德</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">漏保空开建议用中高端（到官网查防伪码）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">灯具选购可以考虑买比较便宜的灯架配质量好的光源</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">花洒、水龙头、角阀等卫浴五金，实体店买可以对比手感</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">网购不建议买浙江地区发货的低端产品（铅超标）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">一般建议选优质全铜材质，有全屋净水可选不锈钢材质</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">厨柜</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">吊柜、地柜、柜门、五金</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">安装</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">注：橱柜可以等油工撤场后才安装、赶工可以同时进行</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">确认台面高度与定制尺寸是否一致、水平</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">电器、拉篮五金与预留尺寸吻合</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">安装完成后检查是否平整牢固</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">对照设计图检查分区尺寸是否准确</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">台面墙面缝隙玻璃胶最好打成小圆角方便以后清洁</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">切菜区最好在背板处加块板，加强支撑效果</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">检查下水接好后检查排水是否顺畅，有无漏水</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">检查柜门、拉篮等五金件是否顺畅无阻</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">合页螺丝一定要打满</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">油烟机、煤气灶、消毒</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">柜安装</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">联系烟机售后上门安装</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">建议用<span>UPVC</span><span>硬管代替软管</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">管道留一定倾斜度避免油烟倒流到烟机内</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">如果是地砖上墙，钻孔要先用玻璃钻头加水避免开裂</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">注意避开水电气管钻孔。</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">有条件可以让水电师傅先装好厨房卫生间面板</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">洗手间厨房</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">吊顶</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">安装</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">如吊顶伸入吊柜，先做吊柜再做吊顶</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">如果吊柜不伸入吊顶，先做吊顶再做吊柜</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">吊顶验收：检查拼板花纹图案、缝隙、平整度</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">边线与墙面、吊顶接缝处要打玻璃胶封住减少水汽进入</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">油漆工进场</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">一般木工油漆先做完再进行墙面乳胶漆</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">提醒师傅贴保护膜或者美纹纸的时候细致点</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">木工油漆施工现场不要进入（大量<span>VOCs</span><span>污染物挥发）</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">木工油漆验收看漆面是否平整光滑光滑无气孔</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">细致检查转角、封边处是否上好漆、无裂缝</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="696" colspan="3">\r\n					<p style="text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal" align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">墙面批灰进场，验收材料</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">刷涂面积可以用套内面积<span>X3</span><span>估算（客厅房间墙面不挂瓷砖）</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">假设套内实用面积<span>80</span><span>平米，扣去厨卫阳台瓷砖墙面</span><span>10</span><span>平米，估算刷涂面积约（</span><span>80-10</span><span>）</span><span>X3</span><span>≈</span><span>210</span><span>㎡</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">腻子粉三遍约需要<span>210</span><span>÷</span><span>7</span><span>≈</span><span>30</span><span>包（</span><span>20kg</span><span>装一般不足称）</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">面漆刷涂两遍约需要<span>210</span><span>÷</span><span>40</span><span>≈</span><span>5</span><span>桶（</span><span>5L</span><span>装）</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">底漆一遍用量约需要<span>5</span><span>÷</span><span>1.8</span><span>≈</span><span>3</span><span>桶</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">毛坯墙基层处理，打磨墙面</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">若开发商刮好腻子，先判断其质量</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">容易掉粉则铲掉重做，难铲掉则保留</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">水泥墙面状态先贴护角线（阴角、阳角）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">第一层找平水泥墙面（石膏或者腻子）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"><span>第二、</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">三层刮腻子到平整</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">打磨腻子层到平整，清理墙面地面灰尘。</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">检查墙面阴角、阳角有无瑕疵，墙面无起泡</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">乳胶漆没有找平效果，验收时要保证腻子层平整</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">没必要全屋挂网，多数是想多收费才这么建议</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">新建墙体由于收缩，很容易开裂也较难避免</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">新建墙体和旧墙交界处、裂缝处贴玻璃纤维网即可。</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">如果有明显严重的裂缝问题可找开发商、物业整改</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">安装室内房间门</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">腻子刮完可安装室内门（建议装配套的门套）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">门锁一般另配，建议用静音锁，容易关且静音</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">如果门后是衣柜等非墙体，门顶可装在地面。</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">安装时天气要注意，冬天留缝偏大点，夏天可以偏小点</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">完成后要多次开关检查是否牢固、吻合。</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="696" colspan="3">\r\n					<p style="text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal" align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">铺贴壁纸</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">胶水主要污染物是游离甲醛，可用鼻子对比其环保性</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">壁纸施工对其寿命很重要</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">腻子墙面打磨清洁后贴壁纸，现场卫生搞好</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">壁纸不能用湿贴法（整张泡在胶水里）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">采用干贴法：单面刷胶后叠好静置几分钟后再贴</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">注意对花准确，边角溢胶及时擦除</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">壁纸贴完后必须关闭门窗阴干，否则容易翘起</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">潮湿、昼夜温差大的天气禁止施工</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">购买墙面乳胶漆、调色</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">调色费用区间大，深色可能到￥<span>300+</span><span>每桶，浅色有时可免费</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">实际刷涂两遍的效果一般比色卡深，选色时要注意</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">乳胶漆系列众多，价位<span>250~400</span><span>之间选择即可</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">过度宣传绿色环保的建材基本都是忽悠</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">刷底漆一遍，面漆两遍</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">一定要等上一层漆干了才做下一层</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">现场不要停留，<span>VOC</span><span>污染物挥发高峰</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">施工环境注意搞好卫生，扬尘严重影响漆面效果</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">国产乳胶漆需要加<span>5~10%</span><span>的水搅拌再刷涂为正常现象</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">地面做好保护，乳胶漆滴在地面卫生难处理（尤其是木地板！）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">提前预约保洁公司上门服务</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">问清楚收费包括的项目和效果</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">外玻璃清洁等是否需要另收费</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">垃圾是否包清理出去</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">窗帘选购</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">选购晾衣架</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">窗帘报价多误区和陷阱</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">窗帘实际用布为门窗宽度的<span>2~3</span><span>倍，</span><span>2</span><span>倍其实够了，部分商家按</span><span>3</span><span>倍长度定制其实没必要（而且米数多数不足）</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">配件价格一般另算，占总的比例可达<span>50%</span><span>以上。</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">有挂钩、吊环、轨道、拼接、罗马杆、管撑等配件</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">问清楚布料<span>+</span><span>配件的总价才交定金是上策。</span></span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">房间强烈建议选遮光布</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">安装开关插座面板</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">、角阀、水嘴。</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">角阀水嘴装好，打开总水闸检查接口是否有漏水。</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">确保开关插座面板开关顺滑，安装水平整齐</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;">带上相位检测插头进行验收每一个插座</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">安装灯具、洁具、</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">浴室柜、水龙头、花洒等</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">五金挂件</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">安装灯具后检查灯具功能是否正常</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">重点检查双控的开关是否工作正常</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">不可在空心砖墙挂浴室柜，与墙面缝隙要打玻璃胶。</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">各种五金件钻孔位置确保无水电走管</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">龙头花洒安装前放掉管道内的带沙的脏水避免影响阀芯寿命</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">龙头花洒安装后一定要试水</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">木地板安装</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">复合地板要注意地面找平和除尘工作做好</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">实木地板注意龙骨下防潮、防虫的相关辅料齐备</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">一般都需要留伸缩缝然后地脚线遮盖起来</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">验收主要检查有无缝隙、起鼓、异响、色差等问题</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">简单的方法就是用脚跺个遍检查</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">定制衣柜安装</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">到顶的柜子可能有缝隙（毛坯房一般都不会很平整）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">后期需要用石膏腻子补缝或者用吊顶、边线进行收边装饰</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">这种情况要提前和刷墙师傅或者木工沟通好</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">如有变形或者碰伤要现场及时反馈</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">对照图纸确保实物与设计无误（尤其柜体内部分割）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="696" colspan="3">\r\n					<p style="text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal" align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">保洁公司上门清洁</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">常用工具：草酸（需要稀释使用）、玻璃清洁剂、扫把拖把、水桶、旧衣服毛巾、长柄刷子、手套口罩等护具、铲刀、美工刀、大号麻袋垃圾袋旧衣服毛巾</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">家具</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">电器</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">进场</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">、</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">安装窗帘、防蚊纱窗、晾衣架、软装配饰</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">冰箱装好后静置一天后才开（制冷剂回位）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">滚筒洗衣机要装在水平的位置</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">变频空调一定要抽真空（抽两次，共半小时）</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">配饰软装可以慢慢增加，避免颜色太杂。</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">室内环保检测治理</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">人造板材释放甲醛是持续过程</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">很难通过一次两次的甲醛治理解决</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">植物和各种吸附型材料量小且容易饱和</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">各种柜门、抽屉、房间门打开换气</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">通风换气效果最佳而且无需花钱</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">土豪可考虑装新风系统打开换气</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">土鳖可考虑大功率风扇进行换气</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style="background:#548dd4;" valign="middle" width="104">\r\n					<p style="vertical-align:baseline;" class="p">\r\n						<span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">开通电话</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">、</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">电视</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">、</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">网络</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#ffffff;font-size:10.5pt;">、天然气</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="background:#f9f9f9;" valign="middle" width="388">\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">提前开通电视、网络</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">电视机到场的时候可以进行调试</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style="text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;" class="MsoNormal">\r\n						<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;">天然气开